{"version": "https://jsonfeed.org/version/1", "title": "Linux \u8fd0\u7ef4\u7b14\u8bb0", "home_page_url": "https://jangrui.com/", "feed_url": "https://jangrui.com/feed_json_created.json", "description": "\u8fd0\u7ef4\u9700\u8981\u7684\u4e0d\u662f\u5929\u8d4b\u5f02\u7980\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u7ecf\u9a8c\u4e30\u5bcc\uff01 feedId:90082981697670144+userId:YiFvZwEv6nYT1MhCcJua8", "icon": null, "authors": [{"name": "Jangrui"}], "language": "zh", "items": [{"id": "https://jangrui.com/", "url": "https://jangrui.com/", "title": "Home", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-12-12T17:23:11+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://jangrui.com/container/docker/install/", "url": "https://jangrui.com/container/docker/install/", "title": "\u5b89\u88c5 docker", "content_html": "<h1>\u5b89\u88c5 docker</h1>\n<p>=== \"CentOS\"</p>\n<pre><code>```bash\nyum remove -y docker\nyum install -y docker-ce\n```\n</code></pre>\n<p>=== \"Ubuntu\"</p>\n<pre><code>```bash\nsudo apt-get install -y d...\n</code></pre>", "image": null, "date_published": "2024-12-12T17:23:11+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://jangrui.com/container/kubernetes/cka/", "url": "https://jangrui.com/container/kubernetes/cka/", "title": "CKA \u5fc3\u5f97", "content_html": "<h1>CKA \u5fc3\u5f97</h1>\n<h2>1. CKA\u3001CKAD\u8003\u8bd5\u7ecf\u9a8c</h2>\n<p><strong>CKA:</strong> Kubernetes\u7ba1\u7406\u5458\u8ba4\u8bc1\uff08CKA\uff09\u65e8\u5728\u786e\u4fdd\u8ba4\u8bc1\u6301\u6709\u8005\u5177\u5907\u5c65\u884cKubernetes\u7ba1\u7406\u5458\u804c\u8d23\u7684\u6280\u80fd\uff0c\u77e5\u8bc6\u548c\u80fd\u529b\u3002 CKA\u8ba4\u8bc1\u53ef\u5e2e\u52a9\u7ecf\u8fc7\u8ba4\u8bc1\u7684\u7ba1\u7406\u5458\u5728\u5c31\u4e1a\u5e02\u573a\u4e2d\u5feb\u901f\u5efa\u7acb\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u4fe1\u8a89\u548c\u4ef7\u503c\uff0c\u5e76\u80fd\u5e2e\u52a9\u516c\u53f8\u66f4\u5feb\u5730\u96c7\u7528\u9ad8\u8d28\u91cf\u7684\u56e2\u961f\u6765\u652f\u6301\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u53d1...</p>", "image": null, "date_published"